&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
 &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm;&quot;&gt;The designated vehicular
     parking space as depicted on drawing&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;18/329/004 - Proposed Plans - 10 Febuary 2020&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;shall be instated within 3 months of the
     date of this decision and retained in perpetuity thereafter. The on-site
     Blue Badge car parking space shall be constructed and marked as an
     accessible parking bay (to be clearly marked with a British Standard Disabled
     Symbol).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&gt;Reason: To restrict car usage and to promote easier
access for disabled persons&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
 &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm;&quot;&gt;There shall be no public
     address system, music system or noise generating equipment used in any
     part of the premises &lt;span style=&quot;color:red&quot;&gt;or within the exterior garden
     &lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;so as to be audible outside the premises or within adjoining
     premises. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Reason: To safeguard the amenity of adjacent residents
and the area generally.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
 &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm;&quot;&gt;A Management and Travel
     Plan shall be submitted and approved in writing by the Local Planning
     Authority within three months of the date of this decision. The Management
     and Travel Plan shall be implemented in full during all times of operation
     and include the following: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&gt;1. Means by which the applicants will avoid
congregation of users outside the site; and &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&gt;2. Methods used to encourage users to enter and leave
the site quietly and efficiently. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&gt;3. Details of how the applicant will encourage users
to attend the site using sustainable methods of travel.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;







&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&gt;Reason: To safeguard the amenity of adjacent
residents, and prevent obstruction of the highway&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top:0cm&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
 &lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm;&quot;&gt;The provision of &lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; cycle parking
